788
00:45:00.047 --> 00:45:01.257
Tudo bem?

789
00:45:01.339 --> 00:45:02.507
Sim, claro.

790
00:45:23.779 --> 00:45:24.822
Socorro!

791
00:45:24.946 --> 00:45:26.448
Oh, Deus!

792
00:45:27.199 --> 00:45:28.701
Socorro!

793
